10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
12. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
13. the person who growsiris is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the person who growslily is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

